title: S12 Ep87: Spiritland: A life's journey of the supernatural and a look at some of California's Central Coast Hauntings
itunes:title: Spiritland: A life's journey of the supernatural and a look at some of California's Central Coast Hauntings
description:
Avia Belle Moon has led a fascinating life, receiving calls, voice-mails, texts and messages scrawled on her mirror from the dead. She shares her experiences and fills us in on a few of California's Central Coast hauntings.

Avia Belle Moon: http://aviabellemoon.com/
